### Gateway API Tests

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8090
@token = your-jwt-token-here

### 1. Login (Public Access)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "password"
}

### 2. Register (Public Access)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "operator1",
  "password": "password",
  "email": "operator1@example.com",
  "role": "OPERATOR"
}

### 3. Test Report Service (ADMIN only)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. Test Logging Service (ADMIN only)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/logs/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 5. Test Animal Service (OPERATOR access)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/animals/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

