Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 9. Test Feeding Service (OPERATOR access)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/feeding/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 10. Test Unauthorized Access (No Token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/animals/
# This should return 401 Unauthorized

### 11. Test OPERATOR trying to access ADMIN endpoint (Should fail)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
# Use OPERATOR token - should return 403 Forbidden

### 12. Test ADMIN accessing OPERATOR endpoint (Should succeed)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/animals/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
# Use ADMIN token - should succeed (ADMIN can access OPERATOR endpoints)
